                            <tbody>
                                <tr><th scope="row">Parameter (<code>p</code>):</th><td id="val-p">0.0000</td></tr>
                                <tr><th scope="row"><code>cosh(p)</code>:</th><td id="val-cosh">1.0000</td></tr>
                                <tr><th scope="row"><code>sinh(p)</code>:</th><td id="val-sinh">0.0000</td></tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>

                    <button type="button" class="button" id="open-about-btn" style="margin-top: auto;">About this Visualization</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="page-footer" role="contentinfo">
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024. Audited to Perfection by CodeAuditor Maximus.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <dialog id="about-modal" class="modal-dialog" aria-labelledby="modal-title" aria-describedby="modal-description">
        <div class="modal-dialog-content">
            <header class="modal-header">
                <h2 id="modal-title">About the Visualization</h2>
            </header>

            <div class="modal-body">
                <p id="modal-description">This tool is a high-fidelity, production-ready component demonstrating a deep mathematical relationship in an interactive format.</p>
                <h3>Features</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Interactive Control:</strong> Manipulate the angle via slider, direct canvas interaction (drag), or automated animation.</li>
                    <li><strong>High-DPI Rendering:</strong> The canvas adapts to your screen's pixel density for crisp visuals.</li>
                    <li><strong>Real-time Readouts:</strong> All trigonometric and hyperbolic values are updated instantly, with accessible announcements for screen readers.</li>
                    <li><strong>Visual Clarity:</strong> Color-coded lines and clear labels illustrate the geometric meaning of each function.</li>
                    <li><strong>Full Accessibility:</strong> Full keyboard control for all interactive elements, live-updating readouts, and proper ARIA attributes.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>You can close this modal by clicking "OK", the 'X' icon, pressing the <kbd>Escape</kbd> key, or clicking on the backdrop.</p>
            </div>

            <footer class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="button" id="confirm-modal-btn" autofocus>OK</button>
            </footer>

            <button type="button" class="modal-close-btn" aria-label="Close dialog" id="close-modal-btn">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
                    <path d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12 19 6.41z"/>
                </svg>
